    <briefdescription>
<para>Represents an object in the world that provides defensive capabilities by reducing incoming hit points. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class implements the Composite design pattern, allowing multiple defence items to be treated as a single item. The composite sums the ReduceDamage and Weight values of all contained items. It can be used by creatures to represent carrying or equipping multiple defence items at once. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
